1. Libraries used:
a. OkHttp - for http requests
b. Picasso - for displaying images 
c. Gson - for deserializing the json data

2. API to get the users
 https://reqres.in/

3. Codelab to understand the recycler view
https://codelabs.developers.google.com/codelabs/android-training-create-recycler-view/index.html?index=..%2F..android-training#0

4. Other components
Progress bar: codepath - https://guides.codepath.com/android/handling-progressbars

5. gitignore: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/16736856/what-should-be-in-my-gitignore-for-an-android-studio-project

6. Copying android project from one folder to another: https://en.proft.me/2017/06/28/how-copy-project-android-studio/
